{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"weak"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNOfflineStorageDelegate>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNOfflineStorageDelegate"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delegate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An offline storage object sends messages to its delegate to allow it to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transform URLs before they are requested from the internet. This can be used"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"add or remove custom parameters, or reroute certain requests to other servers"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or endpoints."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"delegate","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"property","title":"delegate","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"delegate"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflineStorage(py)delegate"},"abstract":[{"text":"The receiver’s delegate.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/delegate"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/delegate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/document